  override val startShort =
    "Imagine a city where whispers of the past meet the beats of the present, a place where you can traverse centuries with just a glance. Shanghai, in the embrace of autumn, is where cool breezes play with colorful leaves, and the metro veins pulse beneath active streets, connecting histories and futures." /
    "As the air becomes crisp and the skies clear, this metropolis invites you on an urban exploration like no other. We'll navigate the depths of Shanghai not through hurried steps, but through the efficiency and comfort of the Shanghai Metro and the unhurried stroll of our feet." /
    "The city's energy is unmistakable, yet within it, there's a sense of welcoming peace, beckoning us to discover its treasures, both old and new." /
    "Let us begin our journey at the illustrious Bund. This storied promenade, known to locals as Waitan, is a collage of architectural diversity, showcasing intricate designs from an era when Shanghai was the jewel of the East." /
    "The balanced beauty of the Art Deco and Beaux-Arts facades line up like old world sentinels facing the mighty Huangpu River. Here, the historical aura of a time when traders and magnates walked these very grounds infuses the air, and we can't help but feel a humbling connection to the countless souls who have also admired this view before us." /
    "Our guide leads us onto the wide, balustraded waterfront, where the cool river air washes over us, carrying the sounds of churning water and the distant rumble of the city. The gentle lap of waves against the embankment accompanies our path." /
    "As we walk, the modern Pudong skyline stretches across the horizon like a futuristic vision, its skyscrapers piercing the sky while their lights twinkle and dance upon the darkening sky. Bridging history and modernity, the river acts as a mirror, quietly reflecting the myriad stories Shanghai has to tell."

